Vim Seminar

.vimrc tweaks
    Options
        syntax on
        set nocompatible
        set smartindent
        set expandtab
        set backspace=2
        Tab Characters
            set softtabstop=4
            set shiftwidth=4
        set number
        set showcmd
        set showmatch
        set incsearch
    Keybindings
        imap jj <ESC>
        nnoremap ; :
        vnoremap ; :
        nmap <F12> :set number!<CR>
        nmap <F4> :set invhls<CR>
    Style
        set laststatus

Registers
    viewing
    register accessing

Macros
    creating/running
    
Tabs/Buffers/Splits
    
Completions
    (Ctrl-n) in-document completion, also through c-style includes
    (Ctrl-x Ctrl-f) file completions
